Questions
Image vs Container?
Docker Daemon?
Namespaces?
cgroups?
Why containers lightweight?
Solutions :- 

1. Image vs Container
Image → read-only template
Container → running instance

2. Docker Daemon
Background service managing:
containers
images
networks
volumes

3. Namespaces
Provide isolation:
PID, NET, MNT, IPC, UTS

4. cgroups
Control resources:
CPU, memory, IO

5. Lightweight
No full OS
Shared kernel
Faster startup
Less memory
